{{zh-forms|[[海内存知己，天涯若比邻]]|[[海內]][[存]][[知己]]，[[天涯]][[若]][[比鄰]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: hǎinèi cún zhījǐ, tiānyá ruò bìlín

===Etymology===
*Literally: If one has a close friend somewhere in the world, that person will seem near despite being in a remote corner of the world

===Idiom===
# to feel a closeness to a friend or loved one despite being separated by a great distance (this phrase is often used when talking about the internet, long-distance phones etc)

